These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, aristoff, siglo, bolivar, chaman, cain, baccarat
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the chaman-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Cigar   | baccarat | siglo | chaman | old-henry | bolivar | aristoff | cain |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca, aristoff, havana, alhambra, old-henry, chaman
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
5. the havana-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Cigar   | old-henry | chaman | pall-mall | aristoff | havana | fonseca | alhambra |

