.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, june, march, october, november, july, september
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Birthday   | september | july | november | june | february | march | october |

