.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
House: futuristic, colonial, farmhouse, wooden, craftsman, ranch-style, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is between the wooden house and the craftsman house##2
2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colonial house##1
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
7. the farmhouse house is the farmhouse house##1
8. the futuristic house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| House   | ranch-style | colonial | wooden | gothic-revival | craftsman | futuristic | farmhouse |

