.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
There 7 different types of food: potato, peas, pumpkin, artichoke, cabbage, garlic, cucumber
1. the person eating garlic is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating cabbage##2
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person eating artichoke is the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating potato##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
6. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating peas##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Food   | cucumber | artichoke | garlic | cabbage | pumpkin | peas | potato |

