2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2   |     3     |      4      |      5      |   6    |      7       |
| Beverage   | 7up | iced-tea | lemonade | soy-milk | sprite | tea | juice |

