.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, ship, snowmobile, car, tram, motorbike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the car is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the snowmobile##2
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Transport   | tram | scooter | ship | motorbike | car | snowmobile | jet-ski |

