2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in may##2
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3  |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Birthday   | may | april | january | december | september | november | august |

